title: INE - CCNA Wireless 640-722
description: The CCNA Wireless video course download for Exam 640-722 IUWNE is designed for engineers who want to learn to install, configure, operate, and troubleshoot small to medium-size Wireless LANs (WLANs). This instructor-led video includes both theory and in-depth demonstrations, designed to teach you everything you need to pass the 640-722 IUWNE Exam. This course is taught by Mark Snow, CCIEx4 #14073 (Collaboration, Data Center, Voice, Security)
